location.fullValue: Allison Plan, The View at Groover's Lake

data.description: Welcome to this beautiful cul de sac craftsman style home.  The main level features a welcoming foyer, a cozy family room a separate dining room with coffered ceilings,and well appointed kitchen with backsplah, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space and a breakfast bar with granite counter tops.  There is also a master on the main with double vanity, separate shower and soaking tub on tile flooring as well as a nice walk in closet.Custom oak stairs leading to the second floor includes 3 spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom with water proof flooring. Laundry room features instsalled cabinets.  New WiFi enabled garage door opener, storm front door, and security door on back. There are 2 A/C units for cooling.  Outside you'll find a brick retaining wall, covered patio with concrete slab and adjustable privacy shade.
